replies.author: iKoumimi
replies.txt_content:
The client has sent too many requests within a certain amount of time. 
如果是正版服请将菜单内头颅皮肤移除或NPC皮肤移除，如果是非正版服。请将catserver.yml配置文件内的禁用更新正版信息打开
